The paper deals with lower bounds on symbolic computation on graphs, which is a topic related to data structures (cs.DS) and logic in computer science (cs.LO). The paper also discusses algorithms for model checking, which falls under the category of programming languages (cs.PL) and formal languages and automata theory (cs.FL). Finally, the paper presents an approximation algorithm for the graph diameter, which is related to control theory (cs.SY).
